    • mouseClicked

      public void mouseClicked​(java.awt.event.MouseEvent e)
      Add the pressed CardLabel to selectedCard List and call the method selectCard of CardLabel but if it is just contained remove it calling deselectCard. Also if the number of selected cards reach the number of the player, it use sendNotification of SantoriniGUI to communicate with the server-side and remove or block the others listeners of the elements of the current window.

      Specified by:
      mouseClicked in interface java.awt.event.MouseListener
      Parameters:
      e - the MouseEvent
